Add ice to your #Nick and Nora glass{} with water and set aside.
Add @gin{30%ml}, @Green Chartreuse{30%ml} and @Sweet Vermouth{30%ml} to a #mixing glass{} with ice and stir for around ~{2%minutes}.
Dump cold water out of your glass and strain cocktail into your now chilled vessel. 
Garnish with an olive or real @maraschino cherry{} and serve. 
